Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.12,0:01:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这事很重要，肯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fad(0,500)\fs40\fsp2\be25\bord3\shad3\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(\fs30)\pos(155.904,638.33)}埃米莉·伯林顿\N约翰·波耶加\N乔瑟夫·米尔森
