Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.04,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,克罗伊，你这样子太惨了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,三天？
