Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也没说
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就这么放了你？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我，呃
